
@base = http://localhost:8000/api/v1


## auth

### register

POST {{base}}/auth/register
content-type: application/json

{
    "name": "test",
    "email": "test@test.com",
    "password": "TEst@@1234"
}

### login

POST {{base}}/auth/login
content-type: application/json

{
    "email": "test@test.com",
    "password": "TEst@@1234"
}


